  "description": "<i>X-Men: Mutant Academy 2</i> is a fighting game featuring characters from the <i>X-Men</i> universe. In this sequel to <a id=\"dcdb8128ab197c237fb410d128a754811\" href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=X-Men%3a+Mutant+Academy\">X-Men: Mutant Academy</a>, six new X-Men characters join the ranks, including Rogue, Forge, Nightcrawler, Havok, and two secret fighters. Six new arenas - the X-Mansion, Muir Island, an eerily lit church and Asteroid M (Magneto's Stage), plus two secret levels, have been added. <br><br>The sequel also introduces a so-called &quot;Cerebro mode&quot;, where the player can check out behind-the-scenes character sketches, costume designs and movie set sketches from the <i>X-Men</i> movie. Professor X himself teaches the player the many moves available to the character in the Academy Training mode.",
